name: 【Concept】Liquid Clothes/Liquid Dress 水裙
description:
Tagger made serious mistakes —— did not tag imgs with "from_side" and "from_behind". So I've uploaded V1-fixed.

Tagger犯下了很铸币的错误——没有给侧面和背面视角打标。于是我传了V1修复版。

=================================

Anime lora of course. Some photorealistic model can not understand fantastic and abstract concept.

显然二次元lora。一些真人模型是无法理解幻想和抽象概念的。

You can try different colors like "blue_theme" "green_dress"

可以试试不同的颜色，比如"blue_theme" "green_dress"

You can add tags such as "waves","sea","water" and "water dress" to enhance features.

你可以用"waves","sea","water"和"water dress"等tag来增强效果。

This lora can also enhance "liquid hair".

该lora还能增强"liquid hair"这个tag。

"sky_print" is also interesting to use together.

"sky_print" 一起用也很有意思。

nude/completely nude will make it quite sexy.

nude/completely_nude会变得很涩。
